# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok cathay pacific airways saturday got its second `` i can fly '' education and community service program for hong kong youngsters off the ground .
# ::alignments
(g / get-02
      :ARG0 (a / airport
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Cathay"
                  :op2 "Pacific"
                  :op3 "Airways"))
      :ARG1 (p / program
            :ord (o / ordinal-entity
                  :value 2)
            :topic (p2 / possible-01
                  :ARG1 (f / fly-01
                        :ARG1 (ii / i)
                        :ARG2 (a2 / and
                              :op1 (e / educate-01)
                              :op2 (s / serve-01
                                    :ARG1 (c / community)))))
            :beneficiary (y / youngster
                  :mod (h / hong-kong))
            :location (o2 / off
                  :op1 (g2 / ground)))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (s2 / saturday)))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok ecuadorian vice foreign minister <unk> lucas said on monday his country will never get involved in the colombian conflict .

      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Iain"
                  :op2 "Lucas")
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (c / country
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Ecuador"))
                  :ARG2 (m / minister
                        :mod (v / vice)
                        :topic (f / foreign))))
      :ARG1 (ii / involve-01
            :polarity -
            :ARG1 (c2 / country
                  :poss p)
            :ARG2 (c3 / conflict-01
                  :location (c4 / country
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Colombia")))
            :time (e / ever))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (m2 / monday)))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

      :op1 (r / read-01
            :ARG0 (s / story

                        :ARG1-of (m / move-01)))

                  :mod (t / tag-01
                        :ARG2 (d / dance-01
                              :accompanier (ii / i)))))
      :op2 (h2 / have-degree-91
            :ARG1 (m2 / motion-01)
            :ARG2 (g / good-02
                  :ARG1 m2)
            :ARG3 (m3 / most)
            :ARG5 s
            :mod (ii2 / indeed)))

            :ARG1 m

                  :ARG0 m
                  :ARG1 (v / van
                        :ARG1-of (r / rent-01)
                        :ARG1-of (p / pack-01

                                          :quant 1

                                          :mod (s / string-entity))))))))

      :medium (r2 / report

                        :weekday (t3 / thursday)))))

# ::alignments
(t / try-02
      :ARG1 (p / person
            :mod (c / country
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Canada"))
            :ARG1-of (a / arrest-01
                  :time (y / year
                        :mod (l / last))
                  :location (m / manhunt
                        :mod (w / worldwide))
                  :time (a2 / after
                        :op1 (u / unscramble-00
                              :ARG0 (p2 / person
                                    :ARG2-of (ii / interpolate-01))
                              :ARG1 (ii2 / image
                                    :ARG1-of (s / swirl-01)
                                    :mod (d / digital)
                                    :poss p
                                    :source (p3 / photo
                                          :medium (ii3 / internet))))))
            :ARG1-of (a3 / accuse-01
                  :ARG2 (a4 / abuse-01
                        :ARG0 p
                        :ARG1 (b / boy
                              :age (t2 / temporal-quantity
                                    :quant 12
                                    :unit y)))
                  :manner (s2 / sex-01
                        :ARG0 p
                        :ARG1 b)))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (m2 / monday))
      :location (c2 / country
            :name (n2 / name
                  :op1 "Thailand")))

# ::alignments
(a / and
      :op1 (s / seek-01
            :ARG0 (c / country
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "China"))
            :ARG1 (a2 / admit-02
                  :ARG1 c
                  :ARG2 (o / organization
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "World"
                              :op2 "Trade"
                              :op3 "Organization"))
                  :ARG1-of (a3 / accelerate-01))
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (t / thursday)))
      :op2 (s2 / say-01
            :ARG0 c
            :ARG1 (p / prepare-02
                  :ARG1 c
                  :ARG2 (f / flexible-03
                        :ARG1 c
                        :topic (m / meet-01
                              :ARG0 c
                              :ARG1 (r / require-01
                                    :ARG0 (m2 / member)))))))
